description:
Iconic Japanese serial Cowboy Bebop starring Spike Spiegel's spacecraft on HEN

is reborned and rendered as voxel style.

The Swordfish II was a remodeled MONO Racer built by Doohan. Originally designed for high-speed racing, 
the craft was given armaments and converted into a space-ready fighter. Spike Spiegel owned and flew the ship.
